id: pm-qfte
title: "GH-458: claim/start-task reject --assignee with an untargeted recovery hint (alias or better hint)"
description: "Dogfood GH-458: lifecycle ownership commands take --author while update takes --assignee; agents try --assignee first and the recovery message never mentions --author. Duplicate check: 2026-05-28 never-block pass predates this; no open overlap."
type: Task
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:cli",gh-issue
created_at: "2026-07-06T08:03:12.744Z"
